snippet.title: 🆅🆁┃"Federation77" from MiroWin. Pre-teaser
snippet.description:
"Federation77" (ex-RU77) from MiroWin. Pre-teaser.
Steam-page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1620410/Federation77/
Released on Steam on October 6, 2022 for HTC Vive and Oculus Rift.

The video uses the song "Black birds", composed by Nautilus Pompilius and covered by Alex Alpidovsky.
Alex Alpidovsky channel - https://www.youtube.com/c/AlpidovskyMusic
